    <h2>Itinerary</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>5–6 June:</strong> Munich – Explore Marienplatz, beer gardens, English Garden</li>
      <li><strong>7 June:</strong> Drive to Innsbruck – Visit Nordkette, Old Town</li>
      <li><strong>8 June:</strong> Drive to Vaduz – Explore castle views and city center</li>
      <li><strong>9–10 June:</strong> Lucerne – Chapel Bridge, lake cruise, Swiss cuisine</li>
      <li><strong>11 June:</strong> Lake Constance – Lakeside walk, Zeppelin Museum</li>
      <li><strong>12 June:</strong> Return to Munich – Final shopping, farewell dinner</li>
      <li><strong>13 June:</strong> Rest day / buffer day in Munich</li>
      <li><strong>14 June:</strong> Depart</li>
    </ul>
